Descriptions.Text:
Deal {1} Arcane damage to an enemy, extracting their anima to Animacharge a combo point for {2} sec.

Damaging finishing moves that consume the same number of combo points as your Animacharge function as if they consumed {3} combo points.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {4} combo points.}

Gouges the eyes of an enemy target, incapacitating for {1} sec. Damage will interrupt the effect.

Must be in front of your target.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {2} combo point.}

Release a lethal poison from your weapons and inject it into your target, dealing {1} Nature damage instantly and an additional {2} Nature damage over {3} sec. 

Each time you apply a Lethal Poison to a target affected by Kingsbane, Kingsbane damage increases by {4}%.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {5} combo point.}

Infect the target's blood, dealing {1} Nature damage over {2} sec and gaining {3} use of any Stealth ability. If the target survives its full duration, they suffer an additional {4} damage and you gain {5} additional use of any Stealth ability for {6} sec.

Cooldown reduced by {7} sec if Sepsis does not last its full duration.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {8} combo point.}

Embed a bone spike in the target, dealing {1} Physical damage and {2} Bleed damage every {3} sec until they die or leave combat. 

Refunds a charge when target dies.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {4} combo point plus {5} additional per active bone spike.}

Strike the target, dealing {1} Physical damage.

While Stealthed, you strike through the shadows and appear behind your target up to {2} yds away, dealing {3}% additional damage.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {4} combo points.}

Attack with your poisoned blades, dealing {1} Physical damage, dispelling all enrage effects and applying a concentrated form of your active Non-Lethal poison.

Your Nature damage done to the target is increased by {2}% for {3} sec.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {4} combo point.}

Sprays shurikens at all enemies within {1} yards, dealing {2} Physical damage. Deals reduced damage beyond {3} targets.

Critical strikes with Shuriken Storm apply Find Weakness for {4} sec.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {5} combo point per target hit.}

Viciously strike an enemy, causing {1} Physical damage.

Has a {2}% chance to hit an additional time, making your next Pistol Shot half cost and double damage.

{FFFFFFFF|Awards {3} combo point each time it strikes.}
